      "span_text": "Using an antibody to PMK-1 protein to analyse which tissues activate PMK-1, as determined by its relocalization to the nucleus [CITATION_1] , we observed that the PMK-1 kinase is activated in the intestine of germline-translation-defective mutants (Fig. 4a,b) ."
